The '''Lonely Five Range''', best known simply as the '''Lonely Five''', was a [[Mountain/Legends|mountain]] range on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Ryloth/Legends|Ryloth]]. The subterranean [[City/Legends|city]] of [[Kala'uun/Legends|Kala'uun]] was located within a basaltic peak of the Lonely Five.<ref name="TEGtPaM" />

[[Clan Fenn]] had a [[Fortress/Legends|fortress]] in the mountains. [[Kh'aris Fenn]] lived in [[Exile (punishment)/Legends|exile]] in this fortress during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]].<ref name="Republic 66">[[Republic 66|''Republic'' 66]]</ref>

During the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knight]] [[Rachi Sitra]]'s [[Eta-2 Actis-class interceptor/Legends|Eta-2 ''Actis''-class interceptor]] [[Lonely Five (starfighter)|''Lonely Five'']] was named after the mountain range.<ref name="SWGTCG">{{SWGTCG|set=Threat of the Conqueror|cardname=Lonely Five}}</ref>

